## Resources & data sources at a glance

| Manage | Resources |
|---|---|
| Directory | `freeswitch_domain`, `freeswitch_user` |
| Dialplan / IVR | `freeswitch_dialplan_extension` |
| Trunks | `freeswitch_gateway` |
| Call center | `freeswitch_callcenter_queue` / `_agent` / `_tier` / `_reload` |
| Conferences | `freeswitch_conference_profile` / `_room` |
| Apply hooks | `freeswitch_reloadxml`, `freeswitch_callcenter_reload` |

Data sources mirror the config resources plus runtime lookups
(`freeswitch_user_registration`, `freeswitch_gateway_status`,
`freeswitch_conference_status`).

## Development

For local development against an unpublished build, use `dev_overrides`
(see the platform repo's `hack/` and `~/.terraformrc`); no `terraform init`
is needed in that mode.
